          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Poker is famously known as a game where the success rate depends approximately 20% on the cards you get and 80% on your skill at mind games. Being able to get into your opponents' heads and read their habits has been touted as the pinnacle of poker experience and the dividing line between a casual and a pro. In ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 2,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Poker Club",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": ", the world’s most famous card game goes from the cassinos to the Nintendo Switch, putting the barriers of distance and technology once again between players.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "paragraph",
        "version": 1
      },
      {
        "type": "embed",
        "url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=puHItd9J2sk",
        "html": "<iframe width=\"200\" height=\"113\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/puHItd9J2sk?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen></iframe>",
        "metadata": {
          "title": "Poker Club Launch Trailer | PC | PS5 | Xbox Series X",
          "author_name": "RipstoneGames",
          "author_url": "https://www.youtube.com/user/RipstoneGames",
          "height": 113,
          "width": 200,
          "version": "1.0",
          "provider_name": "YouTube",
          "provider_url": "https://www.youtube.com/",
          "thumbnail_height": 360,
